            "properties": [
                [
                    "name",
                    "Telegram C2 (T1071.002)"
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "Yayo uses Telegram bots as a command-and-control channel, routing operational commands and operational data through the platform's application-layer protocol API over standard HTTPS. Telegram C2 is resilient and low-maintenance, blending with legitimate business messaging traffic and providing the actor with a channel that is difficult to block without impacting normal enterprise communications."
                ],
